<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَإِنِ اسْتَغَلَّهُ، فَالْغَلَّةُ لَهُ، وَإِنِ أخَذَهُ الشَّفِيعُ وَفِيهِ زَرْعٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>ــ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٢٤١٤ -<span class="c5"> مسألة:</span> <span class="c2">(وإنِ اسْتَغلَّهُ)</span> المُشْتَرِي <span class="c2">(فالغَلَّةُ له)</span> لأنَّها نَماءُ مِلْكِه.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢٤١٥ -<span class="c5"> مسألة:</span> (وَإِنِ أخَذَهُ الشَّفِيعُ وَفِيهِ زَرْعٌ أو ثَمَرَةٌ ظاهِرَةٌ،<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>